items.title: Zen and the Art of Natural Skin Care
items.headline: Creating perfect skin is not enigma. This program will show you how to overcome any skin issues easily and naturally.
objectives_summary: Love your skin from face to toes! Once you understand certain skin issues and why they occur, you will become empowered with the lifelong knowledge of how to correct it.
Save hundreds of dollars on toxic skin care products that simply do not work.  We will show you how to replace these products with organic ingredients from the kitchen, to get much better results!
Identify reasons your skin is in its present condition, and how to remedy anything from wrinkles, eczema, acne to cellulite, sunburns and scars.

items.headline: How To Rise Above It and Turn Your Life Around
objectives_summary: Learn what it takes to believe and trust in yourself - Because a belief is a ‘knowing’ of truth deep within you, changing them is not as easy as affirmations because the same mind that’s believing the limiting belief cannot see itself as wrong.
Discover who you REALLY are - Beneath all the layers of self doubt, the masks of being ‘a good girl’ and the need to please others all the time and leave yourself unhappy and last in the process.

Master your own life on purpose - It's not up to anyone else to take responsibility for our choices from this moment forward and therefore happiness, only we ourselves can do this. Learn what that takes and HOW TO DO IT.

How to set effective long term big hairy audacious goals to take you to your desired future
